@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - TeachToken</PageTitle>

<section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header text-center">
            <h1>About TeachToken</h1>
            <p class="lead">Empowering educators through decentralized technology</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>TeachToken is built with a singular purpose: to create a more equitable, transparent, and efficient ecosystem for educational support. By leveraging blockchain technology, we're removing intermediaries, reducing costs, and ensuring that resources reach educators directly.</p>
                <p>Our decentralized platform connects teachers with supporters worldwide, enabling direct funding, resource sharing, and community governance. With TeachToken, we're revolutionizing how educational resources are created, distributed, and monetized.</p>
                
                <h3 class="mt-4">Key Objectives</h3>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i> Empower educators with direct financial support</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i> Create a decentralized marketplace for educational resources</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i> Provide transparent governance through community participation</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i> Build economic stability through innovative tokenomics</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i> Foster a global community of educational supporters</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card shadow-lg rounded-4 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="card-body p-0">
                        <img src="images/mission-image.jpg" alt="TeachToken Mission" class="img-fluid w-100">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <h3>Why Blockchain?</h3>
                            <p>Blockchain technology enables us to create a transparent, secure, and efficient platform where educators and supporters can interact directly, without intermediaries.</p>
                            <p>With smart contracts, we can automate funding distributions, enforce fair marketplace practices, and implement community governance - all while maintaining complete transparency and security.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="bg-light p-4 rounded-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">The Problem We're Solving</h2>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="problem-card text-center p-3 h-100">
                                <div class="icon-wrapper mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd fa-3x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Limited Access to Funding</h3>
                                <p>Educators often struggle to secure adequate resources for their classrooms and projects, relying on personal funds or centralized grant systems with high barriers.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="problem-card text-center p-3 h-100">
                                <div class="icon-wrapper mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-exchange-alt fa-3x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Inefficient Resource Distribution</h3>
                                <p>Traditional distribution channels for educational resources are inefficient, with multiple middlemen taking cuts and reducing the value that reaches educators.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="problem-card text-center p-3 h-100">
                                <div class="icon-wrapper mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-globe fa-3x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Geographic Limitations</h3>
                                <p>Educational support is often limited by geographic and institutional boundaries, making it difficult for global communities to support educators worldwide.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                <h2>Our Solution</h2>
                <p>TeachToken is creating a decentralized ecosystem that directly addresses these challenges through innovative blockchain technology:</p>
                
                <div class="solution-item mb-4">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-currency-exchange text-primary me-2"></i>Decentralized Funding Platform</h4>
                    <p>A direct channel for educators to receive financial support from individuals and organizations worldwide, with minimal fees and maximum transparency.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="solution-item mb-4">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-shop text-primary me-2"></i>Educational Marketplace</h4>
                    <p>A peer-to-peer marketplace where educators can create, share, and monetize their educational resources, reaching a global audience of learners and institutions.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="solution-item mb-4">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-people text-primary me-2"></i>Community Governance</h4>
                    <p>A democratic system where token holders can propose and vote on platform improvements, ensuring the ecosystem evolves to meet the needs of educators and supporters.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="solution-item">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-shield-check text-primary me-2"></i>Economic Stability Mechanisms</h4>
                    <p>Innovative tokenomics with built-in stability mechanisms to protect against market volatility and ensure long-term sustainability.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <div class="roadmap-container p-4 bg-light rounded-4 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4">Our Journey</h3>
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4>Q3 2024</h4>
                                <p>Concept development and team formation</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4>Q4 2024</h4>
                                <p>Smart contract development and security audits</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item active">
                            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4>Q1 2025</h4>
                                <p>Token presale and community building</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4>Q2 2025</h4>
                                <p>Platform launch and ecosystem expansion</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h4>Q3 2025</h4>
                                <p>Global partnerships and integrations</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cta-box text-center p-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-4">
                    <h3>Join Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>Be part of revolutionizing educational support through blockchain technology.</p>
                    <a href="/whitepaper" class="btn btn-light me-2">Read Whitepaper</a>
                    <a href="/presale" class="btn btn-outline-light">Join Presale</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

